Third-party dependencies
------------------------
`base-convert` depends on packages from crates.io declared in its `Cargo.toml`
files; each retains its own license. The language bindings depend on packages
from their respective registries (PyPI, npm, crates.io, Swift Package Manager)
as declared in their manifests.

This repository does not vendor third-party source. The baseRT engine binary,
distributed separately via GitHub Releases, carries its own NOTICE for the
components it vendors.
